  "description": "<p>SALES ADMIN ASSISTANT</p><p>(F&B in Bedok)</p><p><br /></p><p>Salary $2200.00 - $2400.00/month</p><p>Minimum ‘O’ Level</p><p>Communicate with customers in English and Chinese</p><p>Microsoft office skills</p><p>No experience required as training will be provided</p><p>5 day week (alternate Saturday)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>- Processing and verifying orders, including customers’information and payment details</p><p>- Contacting customers by phone or email to answer queries</p><p>- Maintaining and updating sales and customers records</p><p>- Co-ordinating of customers orders with kitchen and logistics department</p><p>- Directing feedback from customers to relevant departments</p><p>- Supporting the sales department with other administrative tasks, if required</p><p><br /></p><p>Please email resume to : accounts@ohsfarm.com.sg</p>",
